title: Ta-Ta's Pizza
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Pizza, Italian, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Italian TAKE-OUT AND DELIVERY ONLY place with a vegan menu featuring pizzas and sandwiches made with mock meat and soy cheese. Specializes in New Brunswick style food which means lots of unusual toppings. Try the fat gore - teese vegan cheese, falafel, french fries, onions and hot sauce.
